xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<databaseChangeLog
  xmlns="http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog"
  xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
  xmlns:ext="http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog-ext"
  xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog/dbchangelog-4.2.xsd
        http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog-ext https://nexus-public-mdtu-ddm-edp-cicd.apps.cicd2.mdtu-ddm.projects.epam.com/repository/extensions/com/epam/digital/data/platform/liquibase-ext-schema/latest/liquibase-ext-schema-latest.xsd">

    <!-- placeholder for registry data model objects -->
    <property  name="dbname"  value="registry"/>

    <changeSet author="registry owner" id="sbs_list1234567">
        <createTable tableName="sbs_list7" ext:historyFlag="true">
            <column name="id" type="UUID" defaultValueComputed="uuid_generate_v4()">
                <constraints nullable="false" primaryKey="true" unique="true" primaryKeyName="1st_sbs7_id"/>
            </column>
            <column name="name" type="Text"/>
        </createTable>
    </changeSet>

</databaseChangeLog>
